The harder the battle, the sweeter the victory 👑 

For the @pho3nixife Sub8 Project, I will face many battles.
The battle with history,
The battle with my limits,
And the battle with my rival - @nicolaspirigofficial 

This is going to be a whole new push on what’s possible but I am ready to take on the battle and prove what I can do 🥇

#DefyTheImpossible  #Pho3nix  #Sub7Sub8  #Triathlon 
🎬 @mana.studios  @orbitalstud.io |

We’re going to be unstoppable…

It’s been a tough journey to get to this point, a lot of being told I will never achieve the things I want to, that my dreams are impossible…

I’m doing this for my younger self, still chasing the dreams she had. I have a lot more to give in this sport and I’m nowhere near finding my limit.

Watch Battle for Glory now to hear more about my road to the Collins Cup…
